cmcIII.name: cmcIII

revisions.description: added new enums, fixed wrong descriptions.
added cmcIIIFiles, cmcIIIVarByTypeTable, cmcIIIVarIntDynTable, cmcIIIUnitLoadTable, cmcIIIUnitMode, cmcIIICapabilityRev, and all members of cmcIIIRadiusMibGroup, cmcIIIWebCamMibGroup.
extended cmcIIILdapMibGroup, added cmcIIIShutdownMibGroup, cmcIIIModbusMibGroup, cmcIIIDrcMibGroup, added OPC UA support.

cmcIII.contactinfo: www.rittal.de RITTAL GmbH & Co. KG Forschung & Entwicklung Auf dem Stuetzelberg D-35745 Herborn Germany, Europe +49(0)2772 5050 info@rittal.de.
cmcIII.description: The MIB module for representing cmcIII SNMP agent.

cmcIIIMibMajRev.name: cmcIIIMibMajRev
cmcIIIMibMajRev.description: The Major Revision level. A change in the major revision level represents a major change in the architecture of the MIB. A change in the major revision level may indicate a significant change in the information, correct interpretation of data may require a MIB document with the same major revision level.

cmcIIIMibMinRev.name: cmcIIIMibMinRev
cmcIIIMibMinRev.description: The Minor Revision level. A change in the minor revision level may represent some minor additional support, no changes to any pre-existing information has occurred.

cmcIIICapabilityRev.name: cmcIIICapabilityRev
cmcIIICapabilityRev.description: This agents capabilities as used in RITTAL-CMC-III-CAPABILITY-MIB.

cmcIIIUnitStatus.name: cmcIIIUnitStatus
cmcIIIUnitStatus.description: General Status of CMCIII PU unit itself (1) OK (2) failed (3) overload (current too high).

cmcIIIUnitType.name: cmcIIIUnitType
cmcIIIUnitType.description: Type of CMCIII (1) Unit unknown (2) Processing Unit (3) Processing Unit Compact (4) LCP (5) PDU (6) RiMatrix S.

cmcIIIUnitCurrentSource.name: cmcIIIUnitCurrentSource
cmcIIIUnitCurrentSource.description: Current source of CMCIII PU (1) unknown (2) AC Adapter Power Supply (3) Terminal Strip (4) poe: Power Over Ethernet (5) usb: Universal Serial Bus.

cmcIIICan0CurrentConsumption.name: cmcIIICan0CurrentConsumption
cmcIIICan0CurrentConsumption.description: Maximal current consumption required by CANopen fieldbus 1.

cmcIIICan1CurrentConsumption.name: cmcIIICan1CurrentConsumption
cmcIIICan1CurrentConsumption.description: Maximal current consumption required by CANopen fieldbus 2.

cmcIIIUnitUpTime.name: cmcIIIUnitUpTime
cmcIIIUnitUpTime.description: Operating time of CMCIII PU in seconds since an epoch.

cmcIIIUnitMode.name: cmcIIIUnitMode
cmcIIIUnitMode.description: Current status mode of CMCIII PU and all subsystems (1) local init ini progress (2) start local system first time (3) first start delay (4) restart bus system, reread configuration (5) locally online (6) collect all slaves at the bus (7) reorganize bus (8) up and running (9) prepare for sensor upgrade (10) upgrade sensors (11) gentle termination.

cmcIIIUnitLoadTable.name: cmcIIIUnitLoadTable
cmcIIIUnitLoadTable.description: A list of system load entries.

cmcIIIUnitLoadIndex.name: cmcIIIUnitLoadIndex
cmcIIIUnitLoadIndex.description: Index for the system load table. These are the past minutes the load is given for.

cmcIIILastChangeSetup.name: cmcIIILastChangeSetup
cmcIIILastChangeSetup.description: Last change of configuration according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIISetTempUnit.name: cmcIIISetTempUnit
cmcIIISetTempUnit.description: Unit of all temperature values and setpoints.

cmcIIISetBeeper.name: cmcIIISetBeeper
cmcIIISetBeeper.description: Audible alarm in CMCIII unit: (1) beeper is off (general) (2) beeper is on.

cmcIIIQuitRelay.name: cmcIIIQuitRelay
cmcIIIQuitRelay.description: Enable or disable acknowledging currently active alarm relay (with 'C' on CMCIII).

cmcIIILogicRelay.name: cmcIIILogicRelay
cmcIIILogicRelay.description: Logic of alarm relay: (1) Relay will pick up in case of an alarm (2) Relay will release in case of an alarm (3) Relay disabled.

cmcIIIUnitMsgRelay.name: cmcIIIUnitMsgRelay
cmcIIIUnitMsgRelay.description: Alarm relay in case of Device Messages (detect, lost, changed..): (1) Relay disabled, relay will not switch in case of a device message (2) Relay enabled, relay will switch in case of a unit message.

cmcIIIFunctionRelay.name: cmcIIIFunctionRelay
cmcIIIFunctionRelay.description: Logic of alarm relay: (1) Relay will switch in case of a warning only (2) Relay will switch in case of an alarm only (3) Relay will switch in case of an alarm or warning.

cmcIIISetupDate.name: cmcIIISetupDate
cmcIIISetupDate.description: Actual date in format DD.MM.YYYY Use UTC date to set date.

cmcIIISetupTime.name: cmcIIISetupTime
cmcIIISetupTime.description: Actual time in format HH:MM:SS, HH (0-23), MM (0-59), SS (0-59). Use UTC time to set time.

cmcIIIWebAccess.name: cmcIIIWebAccess
cmcIIIWebAccess.description: Web access status: (0) httpEnabled : http protocol is enabled (1) httpsEnabled : https protocol is enabled.

cmcIIILanguage.name: cmcIIILanguage
cmcIIILanguage.description: Language: (1) English. (2) German, (3) French, (4) Spanish, (5) Portuguese, (6) Russian, (7) Chinese (8) Japanese.

cmcIIIOpcUaPort.name: cmcIIIOpcUaPort
cmcIIIOpcUaPort.description: TCP/IP port of OPC UA daemon.

cmcIIINumberOfTimers.name: cmcIIINumberOfTimers
cmcIIINumberOfTimers.description: Number of value table entries=number of outlets available on this unit.

cmcIIITimerIndex.name: cmcIIITimerIndex
cmcIIITimerIndex.description: Index for the list of timer entries. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfTimers.

cmcIIITimerDayOfWeek.name: cmcIIITimerDayOfWeek
cmcIIITimerDayOfWeek.description: Selection of day of week for timer to switch.

cmcIIITimeOn.name: cmcIIITimeOn
cmcIIITimeOn.description: Time to switch on current function, Format: HH:MM.

cmcIIITimeOff.name: cmcIIITimeOff
cmcIIITimeOff.description: Time to switch off current function, Format: HH:MM.

cmcIIITimerFunction.name: cmcIIITimerFunction
cmcIIITimerFunction.description: Function which is controlled via timer 1: Unlock of doors via keypad is disabled 2: Doors will be unlocked 3-6: sending traps to this trap receiver will be disabled 7-10: sending SMS to phone number 1..4 will be disabled 11-18: Scheduled alarm off.

cmcIIINumberOfTrapReceivers.name: cmcIIINumberOfTrapReceivers
cmcIIINumberOfTrapReceivers.description: Number of TrapReceiverTable entries. The number of trap receivers.

cmcIIITrapReceiverTable.name: cmcIIITrapReceiverTable
cmcIIITrapReceiverTable.description: A list of trap receiver entries.

cmcIIITrapReceiverIndex.name: cmcIIITrapReceiverIndex
cmcIIITrapReceiverIndex.description: Index for the trap receiver table. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of NumberOfTrapReceivers.

cmcIIITrapReceiverStatus.name: cmcIIITrapReceiverStatus
cmcIIITrapReceiverStatus.description: Enable SNMP version and trap/inform type or disable trap receiver. Enumeration type snmpv3Inform(6) is not yet supported.

cmcIIISmtpAuth.name: cmcIIISmtpAuth
cmcIIISmtpAuth.description: SMTP authentication usage: (1) disabled (2) enabled (3) enabled with TLS support.

cmcIIISmtpUsername.name: cmcIIISmtpUsername
cmcIIISmtpUsername.description: Username required to authenticate at the SMTP server.

cmcIIISmtpPassword.name: cmcIIISmtpPassword
cmcIIISmtpPassword.description: Password required to authenticate at the SMTP server.

cmcIIISmtpSender.name: cmcIIISmtpSender
cmcIIISmtpSender.description: Sender address (FROM:) of the SMTP message.

cmcIIISmtpReply.name: cmcIIISmtpReply
cmcIIISmtpReply.description: Reply address (REPLY:) of the SMTP message.

cmcIIINumberOfSmtpReceivers.name: cmcIIINumberOfSmtpReceivers
cmcIIINumberOfSmtpReceivers.description: Number of SmtpReceiverTable entries. The number of SMTP receivers.

cmcIIISmtpReceiverTable.name: cmcIIISmtpReceiverTable
cmcIIISmtpReceiverTable.description: A list of SMTP receiver entries.

cmcIIISmtpReceiverIndex.name: cmcIIISmtpReceiverIndex
cmcIIISmtpReceiverIndex.description: Index for the SMTP receiver table. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of NumberOfSmtpReceivers.

cmcIIINumberOfSmsReceivers.name: cmcIIINumberOfSmsReceivers
cmcIIINumberOfSmsReceivers.description: Number of SmsReceiverTable entries. The number of SMS receivers.

cmcIIISmsReceiverTable.name: cmcIIISmsReceiverTable
cmcIIISmsReceiverTable.description: A list of SMS receiver entries.

cmcIIISmsReceiverIndex.name: cmcIIISmsReceiverIndex
cmcIIISmsReceiverIndex.description: Index for the SMS receiver table. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of NumberOfSmsReceivers.

cmcIIISysLogServer1.name: cmcIIISysLogServer1
cmcIIISysLogServer1.description: IP address of first SysLog server.

cmcIIISysLogServer2.name: cmcIIISysLogServer2
cmcIIISysLogServer2.description: IP address of second SysLog server.

cmcIIINtpTimeZone.name: cmcIIINtpTimeZone
cmcIIINtpTimeZone.description: NTP time zone, see cmcIIITimeZone for valid time zones.

cmcIIINtpServer1.name: cmcIIINtpServer1
cmcIIINtpServer1.description: IP address of first NTP server.

cmcIIINtpServer2.name: cmcIIINtpServer2
cmcIIINtpServer2.description: IP address of second NTP server.

cmcIIINumberOfShutdowns.name: cmcIIINumberOfShutdowns
cmcIIINumberOfShutdowns.description: Number of cmcIIIShutdownTable entries. The number of shutdown servers.

cmcIIIShutdownIndex.name: cmcIIIShutdownIndex
cmcIIIShutdownIndex.description: Index for the shutdown server table. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfShutdowns.

cmcIIIShutdownServer.name: cmcIIIShutdownServer
cmcIIIShutdownServer.description: IP address or name of server to shutdown.

cmcIIIShutdownEnabled.name: cmcIIIShutdownEnabled
cmcIIIShutdownEnabled.description: Enable or disable this server shutdown entry.

cmcIIIModbusStatus.name: cmcIIIModbusStatus
cmcIIIModbusStatus.description: Modbus daemon running status: (1) shutdown (2) readonly (3) writeonly (4) readwrite.

cmcIIINumberOfModbusSources.name: cmcIIINumberOfModbusSources
cmcIIINumberOfModbusSources.description: Number of cmcIIIModbusTable entries. The number of Modbus access settings.

cmcIIIModbusIndex.name: cmcIIIModbusIndex
cmcIIIModbusIndex.description: Index for the Modbus access table. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfModbusSources.

cmcIIIModbusAccess.name: cmcIIIModbusAccess
cmcIIIModbusAccess.description: Modbus access for this source entry: (1) noaccess (2) readonly (3) writeonly (4) readwrite This access is inferior to cmcIIIModbusStatus, e.g. readwrite access also requires readwrite status.

cmcIIIModbusSource.name: cmcIIIModbusSource
cmcIIIModbusSource.description: Source to restrict Modbus access. It can either be a specific hostname, IP address, or a subnet represented as IP/MASK (e.g. 10.10.10.0/255.255.255.0), or IP/BITS (e.g. 10.10.10.0/24), or the IPv6 equivalents. The same source can be specified in several separate entries (presumably with different access tokens), and the first combination that matches the incoming request will be selected.

cmcIIIRadiusPassword.name: cmcIIIRadiusPassword
cmcIIIRadiusPassword.description: Password required to authenticate at the Radius server.

cmcIIIRadiusAuth.name: cmcIIIRadiusAuth
cmcIIIRadiusAuth.description: Radius authentification method: (1) auto - not supported (2) pap (3) chap (4) mschap (5) md5.

cmcIIIWebCamUsername.name: cmcIIIWebCamUsername
cmcIIIWebCamUsername.description: Username required to authenticate at the WebCam server.

cmcIIIWebCamPassword.name: cmcIIIWebCamPassword
cmcIIIWebCamPassword.description: Password required to authenticate at the WebCam server.

cmcIIIWebCamNumberofImages.name: cmcIIIWebCamNumberofImages
cmcIIIWebCamNumberofImages.description: WebCam number of images per event.

cmcIIILastChangeOverallDevStatus.name: cmcIIILastChangeOverallDevStatus
cmcIIILastChangeOverallDevStatus.description: Timestamp of last status change of any device connected to CMCIII PU according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIILastChangeNumberOfDevs.name: cmcIIILastChangeNumberOfDevs
cmcIIILastChangeNumberOfDevs.description: Timestamp of last device number change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIILastChangeDevSettings.name: cmcIIILastChangeDevSettings
cmcIIILastChangeDevSettings.description: Timestamp of last setting change of any device connected to CMCIII PU according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime. This timestamp will be affected by SNMP settings only!

cmcIIILastChangeDevs.name: cmcIIILastChangeDevs
cmcIIILastChangeDevs.description: Timestamp of last device change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIIDevIndex.name: cmcIIIDevIndex
cmcIIIDevIndex.description: Index of device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevName.name: cmcIIIDevName
cmcIIIDevName.description: Name of the device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevAlias.name: cmcIIIDevAlias
cmcIIIDevAlias.description: Descriptional text for device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevType.name: cmcIIIDevType
cmcIIIDevType.description: Type of device chassis connected to CMCIII PU. The authoritative identification of the device contained in the entity is allocated within the SMI cmcIIIProducts subtree (1.3.6.1.4.1.2606.7.7) and provides an easy and unambiguous means for determining `what kind of box' is connected. E.g.: in cmcIIIProductChassis (1.3.6.1.4.1.2606.7.7.4.x) the placeholder x is used for 1 : Not Available 2 : Internal Device of Processing Unit 3 : Virtual Device 4 : Temperature Sensor 7030.110 5 : Temp/Humidity Sensor 7030.111 6 : Vandalism Sensor 7030.130 7 : Access Sensor 7030.120 8 : Door Lock Device 7030.200, .210 9 : Universal Sensor 7030.190 10: Sensor Gateway 7030.100 11: Power Unit 7030.050 12: Pressure Sensor 7030.150 20-25: Gateways to RS422, RS485.

cmcIIIDevNodeID.name: cmcIIIDevNodeID
cmcIIIDevNodeID.description: Node ID of device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevStatus.name: cmcIIIDevStatus
cmcIIIDevStatus.description: General Status of device connected to CMCIII PU (1) Device not available (2) OK (3) Device detected, confirmation required (4) Device lost (disconnected), confirmation required (5) Device changed (6) Error (7) Firmware Update pending (8) Firmware Update running.

cmcIIIDevArtNr.name: cmcIIIDevArtNr
cmcIIIDevArtNr.description: Article number of device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevLocation.name: cmcIIIDevLocation
cmcIIIDevLocation.description: Location of device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevBus.name: cmcIIIDevBus
cmcIIIDevBus.description: CAN bus of device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevPos.name: cmcIIIDevPos
cmcIIIDevPos.description: Position (order) of device in CAN bus connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevFW.name: cmcIIIDevFW
cmcIIIDevFW.description: FW version of device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevHW.name: cmcIIIDevHW
cmcIIIDevHW.description: HW version of device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevSerial.name: cmcIIIDevSerial
cmcIIIDevSerial.description: Serial number of device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevProductWeek.name: cmcIIIDevProductWeek
cmcIIIDevProductWeek.description: Production week of device connected to CMCIII PU.

cmcIIIDevLastChange.name: cmcIIIDevLastChange
cmcIIIDevLastChange.description: Timestamp of last change of device connected to CMCIII PU according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIIDevURL.name: cmcIIIDevURL
cmcIIIDevURL.description: URL to device page of CMCIII PU (if available).

cmcIIIDevNumberOfVars.name: cmcIIIDevNumberOfVars
cmcIIIDevNumberOfVars.description: Number of variables available on this device. This variable will give the number of rows of the variable table cmcIIIVarTable belonging to this device.

cmcIIIDevNumberOfMsgs.name: cmcIIIDevNumberOfMsgs
cmcIIIDevNumberOfMsgs.description: Number of messages available in this device. This variable will give the number of rows of the message table cmcIIIMsgTable belonging to this device.

cmcIIIDevCurrentMinConsumption.name: cmcIIIDevCurrentMinConsumption
cmcIIIDevCurrentMinConsumption.description: Standby power consumption of device in mA.

cmcIIIDevCurrentMaxConsumption.name: cmcIIIDevCurrentMaxConsumption
cmcIIIDevCurrentMaxConsumption.description: Maximal power consumption of device in mA.

cmcIIIDevEntPhysicalIndex.name: cmcIIIDevEntPhysicalIndex
cmcIIIDevEntPhysicalIndex.description: Corresponding entPhysicalIndex of this device. 0 if none exists.

cmcIIILastChangeNumberOfVars.name: cmcIIILastChangeNumberOfVars
cmcIIILastChangeNumberOfVars.description: Timestamp of last change number of variables according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIILastChangeVarSettings.name: cmcIIILastChangeVarSettings
cmcIIILastChangeVarSettings.description: Timestamp of last setting change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime This timestamp will be affected by SNMP settings only!

cmcIIILastChangeVars.name: cmcIIILastChangeVars
cmcIIILastChangeVars.description: Timestamp of last variable change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIIVarByQualityHide.name: cmcIIIVarByQualityHide
cmcIIIVarByQualityHide.description: Hide entries in cmcIIIVarByQualityTable to reduce table size.

cmcIIIDynUpdateRate.name: cmcIIIDynUpdateRate
cmcIIIDynUpdateRate.description: Update rate in seconds to add/remove entries from cmcIIIVarIntDynTable and cmcIIIVarStrDynTable. Note: cmcIIIDynUpdateHistory (>0) has to be at least twice cmcIIIDynUpdateRate.

cmcIIIDynUpdateHistory.name: cmcIIIDynUpdateHistory
cmcIIIDynUpdateHistory.description: History range in seconds to restrict data view in cmcIIIVarIntDynTable and cmcIIIVarStrDynTable. The value 0 will disable the history range restriction completly. Note: cmcIIIDynUpdateHistory (>0) has to be at least twice cmcIIIDynUpdateRate.

cmcIIIVarDeviceIndex.name: cmcIIIVarDeviceIndex
cmcIIIVarDeviceIndex.description: Index for the device. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfDevs.

cmcIIIVarIndex.name: cmcIIIVarIndex
cmcIIIVarIndex.description: Index for the list of value entries. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfVars.

cmcIIIVarUnit.name: cmcIIIVarUnit
cmcIIIVarUnit.description: Unit of variable e. g. degree C.

cmcIIIVarScale.name: cmcIIIVarScale
cmcIIIVarScale.description: Scaling factor of variable value, e. g. -100 -> value has to be divided by 100 +100 -> value has to be multiplied by 100.

cmcIIIVarConstraints.name: cmcIIIVarConstraints
cmcIIIVarConstraints.description: Constraints of value, e. g. [-_ a-zA-Z0-9]+ (if VariableDatatype is 'string').

cmcIIIVarValueStr.name: cmcIIIVarValueStr
cmcIIIVarValueStr.description: Value as string, including sign (+/-) and unit (degree C).

cmcIIIVarLastChange.name: cmcIIIVarLastChange
cmcIIIVarLastChange.description: Timestamp of last update or change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIIVarEntPhysicalIndex.name: cmcIIIVarEntPhysicalIndex
cmcIIIVarEntPhysicalIndex.description: Corresponding entPhysicalIndex of this variable. 0 if none exists.

cmcIIIVarByTypeTable.name: cmcIIIVarByTypeTable
cmcIIIVarByTypeTable.description: Headline of variable by type table.

cmcIIIVarByTypeEntry.name: cmcIIIVarByTypeEntry
cmcIIIVarByTypeEntry.description: Entries of variable by type table.

cmcIIIVarByTypeDeviceIndex.name: cmcIIIVarByTypeDeviceIndex
cmcIIIVarByTypeDeviceIndex.description: Index for the device. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfDevs.

cmcIIIVarByTypeIndex.name: cmcIIIVarByTypeIndex
cmcIIIVarByTypeIndex.description: Index for the list of value entries. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfVars.

cmcIIIVarByTypeValueStr.name: cmcIIIVarByTypeValueStr
cmcIIIVarByTypeValueStr.description: Value as string, including sign (+/-) and unit (degree C).

cmcIIIVarByTypeLastChange.name: cmcIIIVarByTypeLastChange
cmcIIIVarByTypeLastChange.description: Timestamp of last update or change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIIVarByQualityTable.name: cmcIIIVarByQualityTable
cmcIIIVarByQualityTable.description: Headline of variable by quality table.

cmcIIIVarByQualityEntry.name: cmcIIIVarByQualityEntry
cmcIIIVarByQualityEntry.description: Entries of variable by quality table. The view of this table may be reduced using the bits of cmcIIIVarByQualityHide.

cmcIIIVarByQualityDeviceIndex.name: cmcIIIVarByQualityDeviceIndex
cmcIIIVarByQualityDeviceIndex.description: Index for the device. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfDevs.

cmcIIIVarByQualityIndex.name: cmcIIIVarByQualityIndex
cmcIIIVarByQualityIndex.description: Index for the list of value entries. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfVars.

cmcIIIVarByQualityValueStr.name: cmcIIIVarByQualityValueStr
cmcIIIVarByQualityValueStr.description: Value as string, including sign (+/-) and unit (degree C).

cmcIIIVarByQualityLastChange.name: cmcIIIVarByQualityLastChange
cmcIIIVarByQualityLastChange.description: Timestamp of last update or change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIIVarIntDynTable.name: cmcIIIVarIntDynTable
cmcIIIVarIntDynTable.description: Headline of dynamically changed variable table of cmcIIIVarDatatype int(2) or enum(4). This table is updated each cmcIIIVarDynUpdateRate seconds only. This table has variables updated/changed within the last cmcIIIVarDynUpdateHistory seconds only. This table has dynamic integer variables (cmcIIIVarDataType = int(2) or enum(4)) only.

cmcIIIVarIntDynDeviceIndex.name: cmcIIIVarIntDynDeviceIndex
cmcIIIVarIntDynDeviceIndex.description: Index for the device. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfDevs.

cmcIIIVarIntDynIndex.name: cmcIIIVarIntDynIndex
cmcIIIVarIntDynIndex.description: Index for the list of value entries. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfVars.

cmcIIIVarIntDynLastChange.name: cmcIIIVarIntDynLastChange
cmcIIIVarIntDynLastChange.description: Timestamp of last update or change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime. Entries may be restricted by cmcIIIDynUpdateHistory.

cmcIIIVarStrDynTable.name: cmcIIIVarStrDynTable
cmcIIIVarStrDynTable.description: Headline of dynamically changed variable table of cmcIIIVarDataType string(3). This table is updated each cmcIIIVarDynUpdateRate seconds only. This table has variables updated/changed within the last cmcIIIVarDynUpdateHistory seconds only. This table has dynamic string variables (cmcIIIVarDataType = string(3)) only. Please note, this table will be empty in most cases as strings are rarely changing.

cmcIIIVarStrDynDeviceIndex.name: cmcIIIVarStrDynDeviceIndex
cmcIIIVarStrDynDeviceIndex.description: Index for the device. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfDevs.

cmcIIIVarStrDynIndex.name: cmcIIIVarStrDynIndex
cmcIIIVarStrDynIndex.description: Index for the list of value entries. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfVars.

cmcIIIVarStrDynLastChange.name: cmcIIIVarStrDynLastChange
cmcIIIVarStrDynLastChange.description: Timestamp of last update or change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime. Entries may be restricted by cmcIIIDynUpdateHistory.

cmcIIINumberOfMsgs.name: cmcIIINumberOfMsgs
cmcIIINumberOfMsgs.description: Number of messages. All status vars available in cmcIIIVarTable will cause a message in cmcIIIMsgTable.

cmcIIILastChangeOverallMsgStatus.name: cmcIIILastChangeOverallMsgStatus
cmcIIILastChangeOverallMsgStatus.description: Timestamp of last status change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIILastChangeNumberOfMsgs.name: cmcIIILastChangeNumberOfMsgs
cmcIIILastChangeNumberOfMsgs.description: Timestamp of last message number change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIILastChangeMsgSettings.name: cmcIIILastChangeMsgSettings
cmcIIILastChangeMsgSettings.description: Timestamp of last setting change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime This timestamp will be affected by SNMP settings only!

cmcIIIMsgDeviceIndex.name: cmcIIIMsgDeviceIndex
cmcIIIMsgDeviceIndex.description: Index for the device. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfDevs.

cmcIIIMsgIndex.name: cmcIIIMsgIndex
cmcIIIMsgIndex.description: Index for the list of message entries. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfMsgs.

cmcIIIMsgText.name: cmcIIIMsgText
cmcIIIMsgText.description: Text for each message (entry in the table).

cmcIIIMsgStatus.name: cmcIIIMsgStatus
cmcIIIMsgStatus.description: Actual message status 1: not available 2: configuration has changed (sensor new, changed, lost) 3: error 4: OK 5: alarm, e.g. smoke, vibration... 6: warning of analog value, value reached high warning threshold 7: analog value too low, value reached low threshold (Alarm) 8: analog value too high, value reached high threshold (Alarm) 9: warning of analog value, value reached low warning threshold 10: output is set to OFF 11: output is set to ON 12: door is open 13: door is closed 14: door is locked 15: door is unlocked by remote input, e.g. external card reader 16: door is unlocked by reader or keypad connected 17: door is unlocked by SNMP set command 18: door is unlocked by WEB 19: door is unlocked by timer 20: no access, wrong key code or card number 21: lost 22: detected 23: battery low, wireless sensor 24: sensor cable broken 25: sensor cable short 26: sensor calibration in progress 27: sensor is inactive 28: sensor is active 29: no Power (PSM) 30: read only (SD, USB-Stick) 31: control boards of LCP exchanged.

cmcIIIMsgRelay.name: cmcIIIMsgRelay
cmcIIIMsgRelay.description: Setup of Alarm relay for this message/alarm 1: no switching of alarm relay 2: switching of alarm relay.

cmcIIIMsgBeeper.name: cmcIIIMsgBeeper
cmcIIIMsgBeeper.description: Setup of Alarm beeper for this alarm 1: no audible alarm 2: audible alarm.

cmcIIIMsgTrap.name: cmcIIIMsgTrap
cmcIIIMsgTrap.description: Each bit is representing an entry of cmcIIITrapReceiverTable. If the corresponding cmcIIITrapReceiverStatus is enabled setting this bit enables sending messages to this receiver.

cmcIIIMsgSMTP.name: cmcIIIMsgSMTP
cmcIIIMsgSMTP.description: Each bit is representing an entry of cmcIIISmtpReceiverTable. If the corresponding cmcIIISmtpReceiverStatus is enabled setting this bit enables sending messages to this receiver.

cmcIIIMsgSMS.name: cmcIIIMsgSMS
cmcIIIMsgSMS.description: Each bit is representing an entry of cmcIIISmsReceiverTable. If the corresponding cmcIIISmsReceiverStatus is enabled setting this bit enables sending messages to this receiver.

cmcIIIMsgQuit.name: cmcIIIMsgQuit
cmcIIIMsgQuit.description: Reset of this alarm 1: auto 2: manual, alarm needs confirmation, e. g. with 'C' key.

cmcIIIMsgVarIdx.name: cmcIIIMsgVarIdx
cmcIIIMsgVarIdx.description: Index of variable 'Status' in variable table generating this message.

cmcIIIMsgVarValueIdx.name: cmcIIIMsgVarValueIdx
cmcIIIMsgVarValueIdx.description: Index of variable 'Value' in the variable table.

cmcIIIDrcIndex.description: Index for the DRC. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfDrcs.

cmcIIILastChangeDrcStatus.description: Timestamp of last DRC change according to operating time cmcIIIUnitUpTime.

cmcIIIDrcSwAntennaBL.description: Software version of antenna modul bootloader.

cmcIIIDrcCommand.description: Command (to) send to the DRC 1: no Quit command 2: Quit command 3: LED auto, LED will show status of TAG (detected, lost..) 4: LEDs of occupied RUs will be switched on 5: LEDs of free RUs will be switched on.

cmcIIITagDrcIndex.description: Index for the DRC. Its value ranges between 1 and the value of cmcIIINumberOfDrcs.

cmcIIITagPosition.description: Tag position within this RU, 0,1 or 2. 0: topmost position 1: middle position 2: lowermost position.

cmcIIITagUnitFormfactor.description: Formfactor of the chassis (number of RUs).

cmcIIITagOffset.name: cmcIIITagOffset
cmcIIITagOffset.description: Tag offset. Offset of the tag related to the topmost position (in one-third of a RU).

cmcIIITagDescName.description: Description name of the unit at this RU.

cmcIIITagAntennaMap.description: Tag position mapping to the antennas. The resolution is one-third of a RU, one RU has three antennas. Position 1 is at the bottom of the rack. This value ranges from 1 to cmcIIIDrcNumberOfRU*3.
